; Conformance test zone for golden-output comparison tests (Sprint 49 task #492).
; Served by both Heimdall and reference implementations (NSD, Knot DNS).
; Records are chosen to cover SOA, NS, A, AAAA, MX, NXDOMAIN, and NODATA paths.
$ORIGIN example.test.
$TTL 3600
@       IN  SOA ns1 hostmaster (
                    2026050501  ; serial
                    3600        ; refresh
                    900         ; retry
                    604800      ; expire
                    300         ; minimum
                )
@       IN  NS  ns1
@       IN  MX  10 mail
ns1     IN  A   192.0.2.1
www     IN  A   192.0.2.2
www     IN  AAAA 2001:db8::2
mail    IN  A   192.0.2.3
